Late night New Year’s Day workout 🏋️. There was only 8 people at this time. This session was mostly weighted rows. I started off with some spikey foam roller and stretching. Opening exercise was 90lb #unilateral incline chest press followed by the 135lb seated rows-also unilateral. The last and final exercise was 5 sets of 3, 55lb #dumbbell Arnold pullovers in which you lay perpendicular across the bench. Do it right and it involves your abs too.
